Features of the Program:

Persistent Storage: Contacts are stored in a JSON file (contacts.json) to ensure data persistence.
Add Contact: Users can add new contacts through dialog boxes for name, phone number, and email address.
View Contacts: All contacts are displayed in a listbox.
Edit Contact: Users can select a contact and edit its information.
Delete Contact: Users can select a contact and delete it.
Graphical User Interface: Provides a user-friendly GUI with buttons for each action.
